<FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">
I just hit 17 and I've been soloing too long. I group with people outdoors and it seems as if I'm playing too much like my mage with nuking and all that. <P>I have read numerous posts that suggest the orcs in HighPass as a beginners guide to crowd control. Roger that, but what are some classic crowd control spell lineups and a typical CC scenario and solution? <P>I ask because I sometimes feel like I did a fine job as an enchanter and other times I feel as if I should leave crowd control to the big kids. Any advice and or strategic discussion would be greatly appreciated. I do have my requisite Steins and INT jewelery, BTW.<P>A humble request from someone trying to maintain the good name of enchanters everywhere. Thanks.<P>--------------------<P>Aan_01 enchanter<BR>Aal_01 rogue<BR>------------------------<BR>"..ha ha, charade you are"
</FONT>
