<FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">
I basically CC the same way as Zanithar (Short stun, long stun, Single mez), If say the puller brings in 3 extras, the way to single target each one (if the puller wont listen to request to back up) <P>Target one that is still at Full hps, Mez, step close and do your short AOE stun and hit esc (to clear target) 99% of the time any thing not on the tank will target you, long stun mez.  <P>On 3+ extras and you feel you have to AOE mez (ack!) then i step back as far as i can (if i can usually not) and AOE mez, i keep max magic res and usually i will resist it if i am in the range.  Now use your quick root and start rooting as many as you can target, as they come free Single mez them. <P> Usually in these situations i break out charm, AOE mez, Charm one, AOE mez, root others, assist lead tank, Pet attack, single mez. <P>Other then that just jump down into a dunguen and get your hands dirty, you will learn quick.<P>Cati Mindweaver<BR>48 Enchanter of Tholuxe.
</FONT>
