No time to type up something fancy, but check out some of the stuff in Eugee's sig, and mix up using stuns, single mez, AOE mez, and root to lock things down.<P>some thoughts:<BR>- mob rushes you, hit ESC so when it hits you you have it tgted, color flux then shift, and mez<BR>- aoe mez centered on the tank. root each mob, and single mez when they wake up (since you can't swap straight into single mez, they have to wake first)<BR>- mouse-look circlestrafe around the fight to get a target, picking them off one by one with single mez<P>spells to have up, maybe:<BR>mez<BR>tash<BR>flux<BR>shift<BR>mesmerization<BR>root<BR>swap (charm maybe)<BR>swap (slow/buffs)<P>g'luck<P>--------------------<P>Andrewe<BR>lvl 57 enchanter, Bristlebane
