<FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">
Standard tactic is to go for the hardest mob first, while you have more mana, and the healer has more mana.<P>As you wear down, and have less mana, the mobs will drop faster after the hard one is dead.<P>The last thing you want to do is have killed 3 or 4 "easy" mobs, using up your healer and nuker mana, and have the big bad mob left.
</FONT>
