Luthian:<P><I>...and my CHA isn't to the point I feel comfortable charming; I should be addressing that soon, though.</I><P>Just FYI, someone recently did a minor foray into charm and charisma (just scratching the iceberg really) but found no difference in charm durations from 85 charisma and over 200!  I'm sure a lot of people will now state that Verant said it helps durations, I'm just bringing attention to something you might check out.  I myself don't find CHA having a massive impact on charming--I suggest testing and finding out for yerself.  Start green and work your way up.<P>--------------------<P><A HREF="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=147058" TARGET=_blank>Sorikk</A> Iksar Master<BR><A HREF="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=41820" TARGET=_blank>Xornn Mier`noen</A> High Elf Beguiler<P><A HREF="http://members.tripod.com/xornn" TARGET=_blank>Xornn's Guide to Enchanting</A>
