Thanks to all posters who have offered advice, tips and general knowledge. I got what I was looking for and that was a general sense of crowd control and some really good spell lineup ideas to experiment with. With my mage, I may swap the bottom 2 or 3 slots, but the top 3 or 4 have remained unchanged for up to 10 levels. With an enchanter, spell swapping is as common as meditating...LOL. I am starting to get a better sense for what my tactics during different scenarios should be, both from advice and my own experience. <P>And Eugee, that site is a wonderful resource for players new to enchanting. I refer to it often.<P>Thanks all.<P>--------------------<P>Aan_01 enchanter<BR>Aal_01 rogue<BR>------------------------<BR>"..ha ha, charade you are"
